## Synopsis
*State what the proposal does in one sentence.*

## Motivation
*What problem does this solve? Why now?*

## Specification
*How exactly will this be executed? Be specific and leave no ambiguity.*

## Rationale

## Risks
*What might go wrong?*

## Timeline
